    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The wall prevents spells from targeting the other side (area effects still cross as normal). Creatures passing through must succeed at a @Check[will|against:spell] save or they are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} for 1 minute; on a critical failure, the creature is instead sent to another plane, with the effect of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.5bTt2CvYHPvaR7QQ]{Interplanar Teleport}. @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.9HpwDN4MYQJnW0LG]{Dispel Magic} can counteract a <em>violet chromatic wall</em>.</p>",
